{"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"DotFaceLite"}],"title":"samSelectDetailRegion","roleHeading":"Function","symbolKind":"func","externalID":"c:@F@samSelectDetailRegion","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"samSelectDetailRegion"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"samSelectDetailRegion"}]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/DotFaceLite\/documentation\/DotFaceLite\/samSelectDetailRegion"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"int","preciseIdentifier":"c:I"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"samSelectDetailRegion"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"const"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"SamColorImage","identifier":"doc:\/\/DotFaceLite\/documentation\/DotFaceLite\/sam_color_image","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@sam_color_image"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"image"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"const"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"int","preciseIdentifier":"c:I"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"detectedObjectBoundingBox"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"int","preciseIdentifier":"c:I"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"selectedBoundingBox"},{"kind":"text","text":");"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Return Value","level":2,"anchor":"return-value"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"0 on success, or a non-zero error code on failure.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Analyzes the input image and identifies the most suitable 200x200 pixel","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"region (bounding box) with high level of details that intersects a given bounding box.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"code":"detectedObjectBoundingBox","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is empty (width or height is 0), any region can be selected. Otherwise,"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the selected region should have non-empty intersection with this bounding box. The selected region","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"should lie fully inside the input image.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If there is no region satisfying these conditions - if image width or height is smaller than 200","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"or ","type":"text"},{"code":"detectedObjectBoundingBox","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" lies outside the image, the selected bounding box will be (0, 0, 200, 200).","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["                                  a bounding box in the format (x, y, width, height)."],"syntax":null},{"type":"codeListing","code":["                                  return, contains the bounding box in the format (x, y, width, height),","                                  where width and height are always set to 200."],"syntax":null}]}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/DotFaceLite\/documentation\/DotFaceLite"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/dotfacelite\/samselectdetailregion"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"references":{"doc://DotFaceLite/documentation/DotFaceLite/samSelectDetailRegion":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"samSelectDetailRegion"}],"title":"samSelectDetailRegion","identifier":"doc:\/\/DotFaceLite\/documentation\/DotFaceLite\/samSelectDetailRegion","url":"\/documentation\/dotfacelite\/samselectdetailregion","abstract":[],"role":"symbol"},"doc://DotFaceLite/documentation/DotFaceLite"